          <td style="padding:0.75rem;border:1px solid var(--color-border);">Near retirement (55+)</td>
          <td style="padding:0.75rem;text-align:center;border:1px solid var(--color-border);">6 - 12 months</td>
          <td style="padding:0.75rem;border:1px solid var(--color-border);">Longer job search times for older workers, health costs rise, limited time to recover</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:0.75rem;border:1px solid var(--color-border);">Volatile industry (hospitality, tech startups, construction)</td>
          <td style="padding:0.75rem;text-align:center;border:1px solid var(--color-border);">6 - 9 months</td>
          <td style="padding:0.75rem;border:1px solid var(--color-border);">Higher layoff risk, seasonal fluctuations, industry downturns can be prolonged</td>
        </tr>
